replies.body:
That would be great, really.. but sadly you'd find a lot of people abuse that and have one player intentionally afk/exit the game in order to grant the rest of the team a free pass.
Adding a huge penalty to the player who afks/exits is a solution but then it just isn't fair for those who genuinely do not wish to leave the game but have internet or computer problems. You can't win either way, I really don't see Rito doing anything or too much about this.. But I do admit it sucks. A lot.
